  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 7120.79 sitting just above the massive +12.6B gamma wall at 7100, dealers are likely selling into this strength as they're long gamma in PIN regime. The thick positive gamma cluster from 7100-7200 creates a powerful magnetic field that should cap upside momentum and pull price back toward the 7100 anchor point. Watch for increased selling pressure if we push toward 7125 (+9.8B) or 7150 (+8.1B), as dealers will aggressively hedge against these levels.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect price to get pulled back down toward 7100 with limited upside past 7150.",
